# Secrets and auth stores: never public
.env
*.env
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/auth.json
**/mcp-tokens/**
**/nous_auth.json
**/*token*
**/*secret*

# Hermes private/runtime state: never public
**/state.db
**/state.db-*
**/sessions/**
**/logs/**
**/cache/**
**/backups/**
**/checkpoints/**
**/state-snapshots/**
**/.hermes_history
**/.skills_prompt_snapshot.json
**/.update_check
**/models_dev_cache.json
**/context_length_cache.yaml
**/memories/**

# Sensitive/private profile runtime content stays private.
# Sanitized public profile packages may exist under profiles/.
**/profiles/**/.env
**/profiles/**/*.env
**/profiles/**/auth.json
**/profiles/**/mcp-tokens/**
**/profiles/**/memories/**
**/profiles/**/sessions/**
**/profiles/**/logs/**
**/profiles/**/cache/**
**/profiles/**/state.db*
**/profiles/**/pairing/**
**/private-profiles/**

# Sensitive/private plugin runtime content stays private.
# Sanitized public plugin packages may exist under plugins/.
**/plugins/**/.env
**/plugins/**/*.env
**/plugins/**/auth.json
**/plugins/**/mcp-tokens/**
**/plugins/**/memories/**
**/plugins/**/sessions/**
**/plugins/**/logs/**
**/plugins/**/cache/**
**/plugins/**/state.db*
**/plugins/**/pairing/**
**/private-plugins/**

# Local build/editor state
.hermes/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
.DS_Store
